# This repo only tracks files placed under it by ./sync. As a safety net,
# hard-block anything secret-bearing or machine-specific from ever entering.

# --- iNiR runtime state (where real API keys + chat history live) ---
**/.local/state/**
**/states.json
**/installed_listfile
**/lastSession.json
**/*.lock
**/*.old

# --- generic secret stores ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*
**/.authinfo*
**/.netrc
**/.npmrc
**/.git-credentials
**/secrets.*
**/credentials*

# --- caches / build junk ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/node_modules/
**/.DS_Store
